body:
the story of us !! part 2 !!

4.26


every song by tay has the upcoming date (4.26) as the background EXCEPT for The Story of Us. It’s now well known that The Story of Us lasts for 4 minutes and 26 seconds which is TOO BIG OF A HINT to be a coincidence, especially since its the only song without the 4:26 background🦋 The queen HERSELF also says ‘next chapter’ at 1:26 in the same song - the number 26 (double 13) pops up again here….

•

Double —> a combination? of both her pop and country roots and styles of music? I reealllyy believe the theory that it was supposed to be released/written between 1989 and reputation, so it could very easily be a combination of all her recent styles!!

•

The Story of Us Part 2 —> many artists do a ‘part 2’ of a song on a later album (aminé with STFU and STFU2 on his more recent album) so who’s to say that taylor won’t do something similar?
